    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-02-12</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-03-06T22:33:06Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>State Video Tax Fairness Act of 2009 - Prohibits any state from imposing a discriminatory tax on any means of providing multichannel video programming distribution services, including Internet protocol technology (or any successor protocol), direct broadcast satellite delivery, and cable television services. </p> <p>Defines a tax as discriminatory if the net tax imposed on one means of providing multichannel video service is higher than the net tax rate imposed on another. </p> <p>Applies this prohibition only to any tax imposed on or after January 1, 2008. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
